title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\HyperparameterTuningJob
name: HyperparameterTuningJob
description:
Represents a HyperparameterTuningJob. A HyperparameterTuningJob has a Study specification and multiple CustomJobs with identical CustomJob specification.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.HyperparameterTuningJob

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

methods.name: __construct
methods.description: Constructor.

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.name
params.description: Output only. Resource name of the HyperparameterTuningJob.

params.name: data.display_name
params.description: Required. The display name of the HyperparameterTuningJob. The name can be up to 128 characters long and can be consist of any UTF-8 characters.

params.name: data.study_spec
params.description: Required. Study configuration of the HyperparameterTuningJob.

params.name: data.max_trial_count
params.description: Required. The desired total number of Trials.

params.name: data.parallel_trial_count
params.description: Required. The desired number of Trials to run in parallel.

params.name: data.max_failed_trial_count
params.description: The number of failed Trials that need to be seen before failing the HyperparameterTuningJob. If set to 0, Vertex AI decides how many Trials must fail before the whole job fails.

params.name: data.trial_job_spec
params.description: Required. The spec of a trial job. The same spec applies to the CustomJobs created in all the trials.

params.name: data.trials
params.description: Output only. Trials of the HyperparameterTuningJob.

params.name: data.state
params.description: Output only. The detailed state of the job.

params.name: data.create_time
params.description: Output only. Time when the HyperparameterTuningJob was created.

params.name: data.start_time
params.description: Output only. Time when the HyperparameterTuningJob for the first time entered the JOB_STATE_RUNNING state.

params.name: data.end_time
params.description: Output only. Time when the HyperparameterTuningJob entered any of the following states: JOB_STATE_SUCCEEDED, JOB_STATE_FAILED, JOB_STATE_CANCELLED.

params.name: data.update_time
params.description: Output only. Time when the HyperparameterTuningJob was most recently updated.

params.name: data.error
params.description: Output only. Only populated when job's state is JOB_STATE_FAILED or JOB_STATE_CANCELLED.

params.name: data.labels
params.description: The labels with user-defined metadata to organize HyperparameterTuningJobs. Label keys and values can be no longer than 64 characters (Unicode codepoints), can only contain lowercase letters, numeric characters, underscores and dashes. International characters are allowed. See https://goo.gl/xmQnxf for more information and examples of labels.

params.name: data.encryption_spec
params.description: Customer-managed encryption key options for a HyperparameterTuningJob. If this is set, then all resources created by the HyperparameterTuningJob will be encrypted with the provided encryption key.
